data.description: Beautiful farm/horse property home located on 2.241 acres of land. This home has 2 horse barns shed/tack room. Great working pellet stove that provides plenty of heat during the winter months. This cozy home has been updated throughout, with beautiful wood looking laminate floors, newer paint, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Bedrooms all on main floors, with spacious master bedroom and 5 piece master bath suite, that also includes walk in closet! This home has a large unfinished walk out basement, just waiting for someone's finishing touches. The opportunities are endless. Long driveway has new asphalt, and plenty of room for all of your toys, animals and more! This is country living at its best!
